title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 3X GTA$ and RP on Junk Energy Skydives
content:
Test your nervous system’s limits by participating in Junk Energy Skydives to land 3X GTA$ and RP. These rewards are doubled to a staggering 6X Rewards for GTA+ Members.

Complete the Weekly Challenge by earning a Gold Medal in 5 Junk Energy Skydives to receive an additional GTA$100,000. Seek out the white parachute icon on the map to jump into any of the 10 daily dives and track your participation in the Interaction Menu under All Collectibles > Daily Collectibles.
